### Pillar 6 ‚Äî Player Monologue

**Expected:** ~15% trigger contextual text injection.

**Actual (main):** `lib/playerMonologue.ts` exists. `data/playerMonologues/class_broker.ts`, `class_enforcer.ts`, `class_reclaimer.ts`, `class_scout.ts`, `class_shepherd.ts`, `class_warden.ts`, `class_wraith.ts` ‚Äî all 7 class pools exist. Dispatch in `_runNarrativePipeline` ¬ßd (`main:lib/gameEngine.ts:1519‚Äì1544`): `shouldTriggerMonologue()` (15% rate enforced inside function), then `generateMonologue()` called with class + personal loss context. Contract ¬ß4.4 invariant: monologue and narrator voice are mutually exclusive per action (one fires per action, not both).

Integration test `tests/integration/monologue-narrator.test.ts` covers all 7 class pools plus trigger logic.

**Delta:** None. Fully wired.
**Severity:** None.

