### Pillar 7 ‚Äî Narrator Voice

**Expected:** ~5% trigger, doubles at high pressure.

**Actual (main):** `lib/narratorVoice.ts` exists. `data/narratorVoices.ts` exists (80+ whisper lines). Dispatch in `_runNarrativePipeline` ¬ßd (`main:lib/gameEngine.ts:1547‚Äì1567`): `shouldNarratorSpeak()` checks a 5% base rate (`NARRATOR_CONFIG`), doubled when pressure ‚â• 6 (per convoy spec). Fires only when monologue did not fire this action (¬ß4.4 invariant). Session tracking via `narrativeSession.lastNarratorAction` prevents rapid repeat.

Integration test `tests/integration/monologue-narrator.test.ts` covers narrator triggers, act transitions, and high-pressure doubling.

**Delta:** None. Fully wired.
**Severity:** None.

